<div class="sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">With people coming from all over the world, connecting over their shared love of a bands music, looking back on old memories and making new ones, it was the perfect setting for As It Is’ triumphant return</p></div>',
  'It’s been close to 3 years since the last As It Is show, and 5 and a half years since the full lineup played a show together. After announcing their comeback last year, re-recording their debut album their first show back together is in the band''s hometown of Brighton with fans travelling from all o',
