<div class="sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">Despite how packed it was (and a noticeable number of photographers crowding the space), it never tipped into uncomfortable. The energy was intense, but it stayed positive. Sweaty, yes—but not quite a bloodbath. (Looking at you, Outpost Liverpool.)</p></div>

