<div class="sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;"><a href="https://open.spotify.com/artist/3hmNB1OCsGQVf8ttZy01e2?si=saFOKDwzRl-r-8_yCQseRA" target="_blank">Big Special</a> clearly have a cult following already—met a couple down front who said it was their <em>ninth</em> show. Based on this performance, it’s not hard to see why. They’re sharp, powerful, and absolutely ready for bigger stages.</p><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">They’re still on tour—if they’re heading near you, <a href="https://bigspecial.co.uk/" target="_blank">get a ticket while you can</a>. These are the kind of gigs you don’t forget.</p></div><a href="https://www.songkick.com/artists/10253312-big-special" class="songkick-widget" data-theme="light" data-track-button="on" data-detect-style="false" data-background-color="transparent" data-locale="en"></a><script src="//widget.songkick.com/10253312/widget.js"></script>',
  'Big Special tore through a sold-out set at Oslo Hackney on May 5, 2025, turning the venue into a full-blown pressure cooker',
