</div>
<div class="sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">Go check out her discography for some fantastic, cinematic and relatable pop, perfect for any daydreaming at the back of the bus- and if you can catch her live! We fully recommend it! </p></div><iframe style="border-radius:12px" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/artist/40L8nrRncQJuunJJ0sEfOz?utm_source=generator" width="100%" height="352" frameBorder="0" allowfullscreen="" allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy"></iframe>',
  'Wrapping Up SXSW London Day 4 we had Coco &amp; the Lost performing an acoustic set at Jaguar Shoes, with a emotional and impactful take on her normal energetic ‘cinematic pop’, she had crips vocals, and great humour between sets!',
