</div>',
  'Faetooth gathered probably the most packed crowd I’ve ever seen in the Arts Centre before, with their support acts ‘Kulk’ and ‘Cwfen’ doing more than just filling time - they were getting the crowd going, ready, and warming everyone up for a brilliant evening (or cooling seeing as there was many fan',
