<div class="sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;"><a href="https://open.spotify.com/artist/0fpdyv56I16Z3FyGnN5xR7?si=GI2_W9dwRbCWmTPHcRWtpg" target="_blank">Kymara </a>is an incredible R&amp;B/Soul artist who works as a collective with her band to create and write a catalog of work that people can connect and vibe with. They have just recently concluded a four week residency at <a href="https://www.casasclub.co.uk/" target="_blank">Casablancas in Brighton</a>. I was lucky enough to experience the magic of show two and four where I got to see them showcasing some new material that they are working on for an album that has been long anticipated.</p><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></div>

