<div class="sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">The first show that I experienced I got to watch the two incredible support acts called Hope Winter and <a href="https://www.instagram.com/chloepamplin/?hl=en" target="_blank">Chloe Pamplin</a>.&nbsp; Both artists were fantastic and jelled well with kymaras music. Both had their own unique style that the audience were mesmerised by which created the perfect atmosphere for Kymaras set.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></div><hr />

