<div class="sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">The second show I attended there was only one support act who used to be one of kymaras backing vocalists called Amanzi. Amanzi is an incredible artist who has just started out in her solo career. This was her debut performance and she absolutely smashed it. The crowd were singing along with her and grooving to her music. The venue was filled from the start not only to see Kymaras final residency show but to also see Amanzi’s debut performance.</p><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></p></div>

