<div class="sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">After seeing both shows two and four of Kymaras residency I was left speechless. As a collective they are one of the tightest bands I have ever seen play live. Their stage presence was captivating and engaging. One of my personal favourite songs that they played is called Elephant Walk. It is a powerful song that will get anyone up dancing. The first time I had the pleasure of working with kymara was back in 2023 and it has been an honour to work with her over this time period and watch her grow as an artist.&nbsp;</p></div>

