<div class="sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class="" data-rte-preserve-empty="true" style="white-space:pre-wrap;"></p><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">After seeing and hearing the new material that Kymara and her band have been working on I can not wait to see where it goes next. Kymara is an incredible artist that commands the stage like no one I have ever seen before, her and her collective work together in perfect harmony and I would recommend that you listen to them as I can see them going on to great things.&nbsp;</p></div>',
  'Kymara is an incredible R&amp;B/Soul artist who works as a collective with her band to create and write a catalog of work that people can connect and vibe with. They have just recently concluded a four week residency at Casablancas in Brighton',
