   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1762168713900-UQ8PB5UR1B09YSIGTPWJ/%40TJEPhotos_+-+Great+Silkie+-+shacklewell+arms+-+14-10-2025+-+010.jpg?format=original" />
  

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1762168714068-B4PM413ID17Q1XX46MMJ/%40TJEPhotos_+-+Great+Silkie+-+shacklewell+arms+-+14-10-2025+-+011.jpg?format=original" />
  

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1762168714940-OHY4H8KSUZ0R01EBQT71/%40TJEPhotos_+-+Great+Silkie+-+shacklewell+arms+-+14-10-2025+-+013.jpg?format=original" />
  

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1762168715351-WEKB57CK0XUH7YU7YPEV/%40TJEPhotos_+-+Great+Silkie+-+shacklewell+arms+-+14-10-2025+-+014.jpg?format=original" />
  

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1762168716086-4JPO0YY1FHQPJ4SOWPBR/%40TJEPhotos_+-+Great+Silkie+-+shacklewell+arms+-+14-10-2025+-+015.jpg?format=original" />
  

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1762168716394-YS25AZ8P5Z9VPBQAB2P4/%40TJEPhotos_+-+Great+Silkie+-+shacklewell+arms+-+14-10-2025+-+016.jpg?format=original" />
  

</div>
<div class="sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">The night started with Great Silkie, who opened the stage and warmed the audience with slow and grungy blankets of sound. With meandering melodies and chunky basslines their whole set swallowed the room in an aura of longing and nostalgia. All accumulating into a finale of noise, thrashy drums and melodies, that once meandered, instead screaming with distortion - Creating a sundae of shoegaze atmospheric beauty.&nbsp;</p></div><hr />

