<div class="sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">Before Orchards took the stage the room had filled out with a crowd of fans right by the stage. Opening with the first track of the new album ‘Say It’, it had people immediately moving and singing along. While the set was a celebration of the new album the band made sure to play older fan favourites as well. With energy high on and off stage, there was a more mellow and emotional moment during song ‘Bethnal Green’ before they picked the energy right back up.&nbsp;</p></div>

