   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1746695994955-08IHP3FWZXM5BE1UHVS2/%40c.shoots.shows+-+Pagent+Mum+-+The+Garage-+04-05-2025+%288%29.jpg?format=original" />
  

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1746695996054-RIONECCM44BDCS5SU8J8/%40c.shoots.shows+-+Pagent+Mum+-+The+Garage-+04-05-2025+%289%29.jpg?format=original" />
  

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1746695996171-B99RB1PZQYT5SK0EE6RR/%40c.shoots.shows+-+Pagent+Mum+-+The+Garage-+04-05-2025+%2810%29.jpg?format=original" />
  

</div>
<hr /><div class="sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">Shed came on stage with a group of people chanting their name, clearly with a lot of fans in the crowd already. With a ton of enthusiastic singalongs it was a very high energy set, only slowly down briefly part way through before picking it back up again. A highlight was their song ‘Lazy Susan’ a song all about Aldi which was clearly a fan favourite in the crowd.</p></div>

<div class="image-gallery-wrapper">

  
