   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1746696069214-NC82LN274VS2K4KQCCW9/%40c.shoots.shows+-+Shed+-+The+Garage-+04-05-2025++%285%29.jpg?format=original" />
  

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1746696069208-4EE9YM2RFH19WO1VAS50/%40c.shoots.shows+-+Shed+-+The+Garage-+04-05-2025++%286%29.jpg?format=original" />
  

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1746696070155-O2BKMLTIPCSIQGJO8WTG/%40c.shoots.shows+-+Shed+-+The+Garage-+04-05-2025++%287%29.jpg?format=original" />
  

</div>
<hr /><div class="sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;"><a href="https://open.spotify.com/artist/3ccF37QB6LC4LqUfvtn5qb?si=euKw5uUMSCqQ0_wUnSxijg" target="_blank">Sonic Boom Six</a> burst onto the stage with a ton of energy, with a non-stop set. With a strong Ska influence there was a ton of movement both on and off the stage. There was a strong upbeat and positive vibe. The energy was truly warming up the crowd before the main event of the night. </p></div>

<div class="image-gallery-wrapper">

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1746696221836-8TQ366DXCO6NPHJZOAAM/%40c.shoots.shows+-+Sonic+Boom+Six-+The+Garage-+04-05-2025++%288%29.jpg?format=original" />
  

  
