   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1747080663303-9TQW10ABHKY326KJHFYQ/%40shardsoflight_+-+South-of-Salem+-+Roxoff+Festival+04-05-2025+%288%29.jpg?format=original" />
  

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1747080663745-BJUQQHGZGR2TZU7661DM/%40shardsoflight_+-+South-of-Salem+-+Roxoff+Festival+04-05-2025+%289%29.jpg?format=original" />
  

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1747080664715-W69DNAHQ7Z4MLMGW1V02/%40shardsoflight_+-+South-of-Salem+-+Roxoff+Festival+04-05-2025+%2810%29.jpg?format=original" />
  

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1747080665706-GRJ3I4FT4S1RD32YEMQS/%40shardsoflight_+-+South-of-Salem+-+Roxoff+Festival+04-05-2025+%2811%29.jpg?format=original" />
  

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1747080666115-9T1YACZ92YYD0K819YVR/%40shardsoflight_+-+South-of-Salem+-+Roxoff+Festival+04-05-2025+%281%29.jpg?format=original" />
  

</div>
<div class="sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;"><em>“Performing banger after banger never slowing up so they can fit in their whole set before the dreaded 11pm curfew, the fans enjoyed every last second of the music, with the energetic crowd singing along to their every word and not wanting the show to end, a packed room for the band.”<br><br></em><br>If You missed out on Catching them at Roxoff- Tickets for Bloodstock are still available from the<a href="https://bloodstock.seetickets.com/event/bloodstock/catton-park/3131566#op1"> <span style="text-decoration:underline">official Bloodstock website</span></a>! Or Check out Our BloodStock 2025 Ones-to-Watch Playlist:</p></div><iframe style="border-radius:12px" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/playlist/28Zj8kFDYnHLQc144GiPT0?utm_source=generator" width="100%" height="352" frameBorder="0" allowfullscreen="" allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy"></iframe>',
  'ROXOFF is an action packed indoor festival at the Brickmakers in Norwich, which started at 14:30 and didn’t end until gone 23:00; with the crowd never wavering.',
