   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1753966775898-S8ZAS9BOPBD9PZNIHCW1/%40nerina.photography+-+Asomvel+-+O2+Ritz+-+30-07-2025+-+007.jpg?format=original" />
  

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1753966776949-3IVWDHVRZ3JJ9SDGMFO1/%40nerina.photography+-+Asomvel+-+O2+Ritz+-+30-07-2025+-+008.jpg?format=original" />
  

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1753966776985-SPHVYMO4KE3CYWA82V8D/%40nerina.photography+-+Asomvel+-+O2+Ritz+-+30-07-2025+-+009.jpg?format=original" />
  

</div>
<div class="sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">Opening the evening, Asomvel hit the stage with raw glam rock swagger—frenzied energy, big riffs, and full-on crowd engagement. Their chemistry was infectious, and they wrapped up their set with a theatrical bow that felt just right. You could tell they were having a blast.</p><p class="" data-rte-preserve-empty="true" style="white-space:pre-wrap;"></p><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">Then came Wolfmother, and over 20 years of stagecraft kicked in immediately. People often say they were a band born in the wrong era, but they''ve more than passed the test of time. Their signature 2000s-style riffs and tight drum fills had the whole room clapping in sync like a metronome. The vocals were razor sharp, and when the unmistakable intro to “Woman” kicked in, the crowd erupted. Pure rock nostalgia, flawlessly delivered.</p></div>

<div class="image-gallery-wrapper">

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1753966803225-FSVCVWS2US5PSXRO7R2F/%40nerina.photography+-+Wolfmother+-+O2+Ritz+-+30-07-2025+-+005.jpg?format=original" />
  

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1753966803339-7N6T557AJF0JZA2OBH26/%40nerina.photography+-+Wolfmother+-+O2+Ritz+-+30-07-2025+-+006.jpg?format=original" />
  

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1753966804358-QI3WM9CZ5HQJ6YDD8O77/%40nerina.photography+-+Wolfmother+-+O2+Ritz+-+30-07-2025+-+007.jpg?format=original" />
  

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1753966804454-HF7A7BTW47N2NLGFE0Z7/%40nerina.photography+-+Wolfmother+-+O2+Ritz+-+30-07-2025+-+008.jpg?format=original" />
  

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1753966805530-VEUU8BHFC1J85SJ1UW4W/%40nerina.photography+-+Wolfmother+-+O2+Ritz+-+30-07-2025+-+001.jpg?format=original" />
  

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1753966805576-YX92N9PQEEC8NA5GS99K/%40nerina.photography+-+Wolfmother+-+O2+Ritz+-+30-07-2025+-+002.jpg?format=original" />
  

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1753966806665-R0PI1VV0DQQKMT5BW3QF/%40nerina.photography+-+Wolfmother+-+O2+Ritz+-+30-07-2025+-+003.jpg?format=original" />
  

  
   <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/627907a6b74722549de2ec0c/1753966806716-Z5XW449VHWF0P7ZQ02ZS/%40nerina.photography+-+Wolfmother+-+O2+Ritz+-+30-07-2025+-+004.jpg?format=original" />
  

</div>',
  '&nbsp;Wolfmother, and over 20 years of stagecraft kicked in immediately. People often say they were a band born in the wrong era, but they''ve more than passed the test of time. Their signature 2000s-style riffs and tight drum fills had the whole room clapping in sync like a metronome.',
